WEBVTT

00:01:28.423 --> 00:01:30.617
Kirurg koristi ovaj instrument

00:01:30.617 --> 00:01:32.033
tako da ga uzme

00:01:32.033 --> 00:01:34.000
i pritisne u trbuh

00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:37.255
sve dok ga ne probuši.

00:01:37.255 --> 00:01:40.327
Razlog zašto su svi u operacijskoj sali

00:01:40.327 --> 00:01:42.974
zurili u taj instrument tog dana

00:01:42.974 --> 00:01:46.205
bio je što je kirurg morao 
neizmjerno paziti

00:01:46.205 --> 00:01:47.672
da njime

00:01:47.672 --> 00:01:51.613
ne ošteti organe i žile.

00:01:51.613 --> 00:01:53.452
Ovaj problem bi svima vama 
trebao biti poznat

00:01:53.452 --> 00:01:56.373
jer sam siguran da ste ga 
već negdje imali.

00:01:56.373 --> 00:01:58.165
(Smijeh)

00:01:58.165 --> 00:01:59.821
Sjećate li se ovoga?

00:01:59.821 --> 00:02:03.937
(Pljesak)